data.description: Take a look at this Updated 5 bed, 3 bath Ranch on 5.89 Acres of beautiful land! New vinyl plank throughout, 2 New HVAC units, new paint, new lights, new windows, new gutters. Welcoming wood-burning fireplace in the family room, split floor plan with a private master suite, updated kitchen with beautiful wood cabinets & 2 pantries, office/library room, additional living room/kids play/teen area,  loads of closet space, mud room & laundry located just off the garage. With fencing around the property and mature pecan trees, make this your own mini farm!
